### Navigation Projection V2 API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@appInstanceId = 1
@appKey = demo

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 平台导航投影
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/navigation/platform
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 预期：groups 中包含 monitor 分组，且有 /console/appbridge/* 三个入口

### 应用工作台导航投影
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/navigation/apps/{{appInstanceId}}/workspace
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 应用工作台导航投影（按 appKey）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/navigation/apps/by-key/{{appKey}}/workspace
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 运行态导航投影
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/navigation/runtime
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
